### Deploy tool scripts
Those scripts are used as wrapper, which sets appropiate APPLICATION_STORE env
 * exec_foreach_store   - executes command given as parameter for each store
 * exec_default_store   - executes command given as parameter once, for first store only

### Cronjobs installed by deployment
 * cron_update_memcache     - minutely cronjob for indexing memcache datastore (installed by enable_local_cronjobs)
 * cron_update_solr         - minutely cronjob for reindexing solr master (installed by enable_cronjobs)

### Monitoring scripts
 * cron_monitor_fatals

### Deployment tasks
Execution order is preserved

   NAME                         EXECUTES ON       USER
 * prepare_code                 deploy host       root
 * check_configuration          all appservers    www
 * configure_host               all appservers    www
 * check_for_migrations         admin host        root (returns: have_migrations?)
 * disable_cronjobs             admin host        root
 * disable_local_cronjobs       all appservers    root
 * enable_maintenance           all appservers    www, only if have_migrations?
--------- offline ---------
 * perform_migrations           admin host        www, only if have_migrations?
 * disable_maintenance          all appservers    www
--------- online ---------
 * initialize_database          admin host        www
--------- new release activated ----------
 * reindex_solr                 admin host        www (only if full_reindex?)
 * reindex_memcache             all appservers    www (only if full_reindex?)
 * enable_cronjobs              admin_host        www
 * enable_local_cronjobs        all appservers    www
 * send_notifications           admin host        www

